object.customQuery:
select policy_source_system_id, policy_number,
policy_cmm_container, insured_name,stp_api_data_transfer_to_guidewire_status,
task_system_id, task_id,
stp_api_data_id
from operations.straight_through_processing_api_data
where
stp_api_data_transfer_to_guidewire_status in ('Confirmed by API', 'Failed')
order by policy_source_system_id desc

object.customQuery:
select t.SystemId, t.Id
from task t
join advrxxchangedbeans a 
on t.SystemId = a.SystemId 
and t.CMMContainer = a.CMMContainer 
where t.TemplateId in ('ReviewNewBusiness-Policy',
'HighPriorityReviewNewBusiness-Policy')
